data.description: 2 story, all bedrooms and laundry upstairs. Kitchen,l with island, gas range, breakfast and dining room. Open floor from dining to living room.  2 car garage - ceiling approx 12 ft high. Wrought iron staircase. 1/2 bath ( powder room) downstairs.
data.whatILove: Quiet friendly neighborhood, easy access to Downtown Helotes and close to San Antonio. Peaceful, and well maintained.
